messages.text: Hurry!! You need to get the tablet!
Okay okay. Hang in there. I’m in the Sciences building.
You have to make sure no one can see you.
We can’t risk the Prof’s top secret research getting out there.
Remember, you and I are the only ones who know about it.
Those annoying sorority girls from class. They’re hanging in the hall.
The ones with the ugly boots and the yoga pants.
Well isn’t that something. They didn’t even look up from their phones.
Must be my head messing with me
Just feels like I’m not alone
Kam turns around to see Tucker swaggering down the hall.
Whoa. Tucker. I didn’t see you there.
And please don’t call me K-Dawg.
No prob, K-Dawg! What you doing here this late?
Nothing, man. I was about to -
You hear any updates on your crazy chick?
Again. Lucy is neither mine nor crazy.
But no, I haven’t heard anything.
Man, she’s in so much trouble
U realize how expensive that car is?
My dad invested a metric butt ton of dollars in the R&D.
And the Prof’s gonna be so pissed.
Speaking of, he wasn’t in class today. You know where he’s at?
Hmm. No idea.  Maybe he had some car troubles.
U okay, dude? You’re acting strange. All nervous and stuff.
Got a hot date or something?
No, just got some things I gotta take care of.
Okay, dude. I’ll be seein’ u soon.  Stay out of trouble, K-Dawg.
Oh man, Lucy. That was close.
And the stupid boat shoes that he wears when NOT ON BOATS?
Yeah, well, I ran into him.
NO ONE CAN KNOW ABOUT THIS.
This is bad. This is bad.
Prof’s lab is right around the corner.
Campus security. Standing outside the lab.
This is bad. I can’t go in.
Like they could leave a bruise.
Oh come on! It’s not that bad.
Man up and figure it out!
Look. I said I’d help, but I’m in WAY over my head here.
I suck at all this sneaky adventure stuff.
That’s why I went into programming
So I could sit inside and quietly avoid excitement.
I went to you because you’re my friend.
And you’re so smart.  I just know you’ll think of something ...
Wait. Programming. That gives me an idea.
Kam runs up to the security guards. He’s got a plan.
I just saw some minors doing some underage drinking!
Seems innocent, but you never know. What if they’re having a good time?
C’mon, Don, let’s go bust some undergrad ass!
If there’s one thing campus security is programmed to do -
The guards ran off. I’m in the clear
I got five minutes tops before someone knows I’m here.
Alright. Looking for the tablet. But it’s dark in here
And this place is a hot mess.
There’s a weird vibe in here - I don’t like this.
Do you remember where he keeps it?
I think it’s in his drawer.
He’s got his arm around you.
Ewww. What’s Prof doing with that pic?
You sure nothing was going on with you two?
Cause he does have that sexy slightly old man vibe
A little bit of that dashing silver fox.
And there was NOTHING going on.
Then maybe he was creepin’ on you and you didn’t even know it
Wait, I think I found it.
Everything is going to be okay.
Hold up. Lemme make sure it’s working
Just get the tablet out of there.
Why did I go along with this?
Kam, just make a break for it
